程序包 factory

This is the package for all classes related to the maze factory This class contains the supporting classes to build a map factory. various map classes extending the same parent class are here connected to the maze factory.

请参阅: 说明

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Drawable
    This interface Drawable defines the basic functions a maze should have Provided by Group, Color
    This interface Drawable defines the basic functions a maze should have.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Maze
    Class Maze is the parent class of all mazes in the pacman game.
    Maze00
    Class Maze00 represents a concrete map in the pacman game provided by HashSet, Set, Group, Color.
    Maze01
    Class Maze01 represents a concrete map in the pacman game provided by HashSet, Set, Group, Color.
    Maze02
    Class Maze00 represents a concrete map in the pacman game provided by HashSet, Set, Group, Color.
    MazeFactory
    Class MazeFactory is the integration class of maps no external package is imported
    This class is the integration class of the factory design pattern for mazes.

程序包factory的说明

This is the package for all classes related to the maze factory

This class contains the supporting classes to build a map factory. various map classes extending the same parent class are here connected to the maze factory.
